STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Donald THOMAS, a/k/a D-Block, and Donald Thomas, III, Defendant-Petitioner, C-999 September Term 2018
082299 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 13, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002032-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
